726841f-c.text:
Hawtree Creek Rd., north from One Hundred Thirty-fifth Ave. to One Hundred Thirty-third Ave., showing in a set of three views on the west side of the road in line of Lefferts Boulevard, the J. H. Lott house of 1860 to 1873, subsequently acquired by William Hopkins.  Richard Wakefield owned it in 1934.

1922
Views 1, 2, and 3.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
